    <section>
        <title>Change section display order in a section form</title>
        <para>You can control in which order sections are displayed in a section form.</para>
        <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>Open the <emphasis role="bold">Maintenance</emphasis> app and click <emphasis
                        role="bold">Data set</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold">Data
                    set</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the list, find the data set you want to edit the section form for.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click the options menu and select <emphasis role="bold">Manage
                        sections</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the list, find the section you want to move.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click the options menu and select <emphasis role="bold">Move up</emphasis> or
                        <emphasis role="bold">Move down</emphasis>.</para>
                <para>If the section you want to move is the first or last section in the list,
                    you'll only see one of the move options.</para>
            </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
    </section>
